title: Neato Burrito - Scottsdale Plaza
typeOfFood: Lacto, Fast food, Take-out, Tex-Mex, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Mission style burrito fast food joint with several locations in Pennsylvania. Build-your-own burrito with seven kinds tortilla choices. Options includes fresh veggies, BBQ or brown rice, black or refried beans, 3 salsas, black bean hummus, and guacamole. Vegans to specify (no sour cream, etc.).
